item.title: Razvan Avramescu
item.description: Razvan is a fan of using continuous integration while architecting the infrastructure for Magento 2-based sites. All in all, Razvan is a veteran Magento 1 and 2 developer who has hands-on experience with bug-fixing, optimization, and module creation.
